               <p>I have known Williams about two years, never heard anything but what was very honest, binding shoes, and needle work.</p>
               <p>The prisoner called one more witness who had known her fifteen years, and gave her a good character.</p>
               <p>BOTH <rs id="t17850629-43-verdict207" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17850629-43-verdict207" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17850629-43-verdict207" type="verdictSubcategory" value="lesserOffence"></interp>
               GUILTY. Of stealing, but not privately
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
